          </h1>
          <p className="text-xl text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light leading-relaxed">
            Propiedades exclusivas sincronizadas en tiempo real con CRM Gvamax.
          </p>
        </header>

        {/* Filters Section */}
        <div className="space-y-4 mb-12">
          <div className="bg-white p-4 md:p-6 rounded-[3rem] shadow-2xl shadow-blue-900/5 border border-slate-100">
            <div className="flex flex-col gap-4">
              <div className="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-3 items-center w-full">
                <div className="flex-[4] relative w-full">
                  <svg className="w-5 h-5 absolute left-6 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-slate-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z" />
                  </svg>
                  <input 
                    type="text" 
                    placeholder="Barrio, calle o referencia..."
                    className="w-full pl-14 pr-6 py-5 bg-slate-50 border border-blue-50 rounded-[2rem] focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-500/10 transition-all outline-none text-slate-700 font-medium"
